### Example Usage:
# 1. Upload an image using the first endpoint
# 2. Use the preview URL in your frontend for displaying images in browser
# 3. Use the download URL when you want to force download
# 4. Use contract URLs for sensitive documents (1 hour expiration)
# 5. Use public document URLs for non-sensitive files (30 days expiration)
# 6. Use temporary URLs for very short-lived access (15 minutes)

### Security Considerations:
# - Contracts: 1 hour expiration for maximum security
# - Public Documents: 30 days for convenience
# - Images: 7 days for normal usage
# - Temporary: 15 minutes for one-time access
